! JSON Convert

A TiddlyWiki plugin that turns arbitrary JSON into tiddlers, with
reusable mapping profiles, a preview-and-commit staging area, and
tolerant input handling.

This is the demo wiki.  The plugin is loaded, six sample profiles
and their matching data are pre-installed, and the Console is one
click away.

! Try it

Click the {{$:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/icon}} icon in the
page-controls toolbar (top-right of the page), or open
[[JSON Convert Console]] directly.

Workflow: paste matching JSON into the source area, pick a profile,
click ''Convert'', review the staged tiddlers, click ''Apply''.

! Samples included

Six profiles, each with a matching data tiddler.  Many-to-many in
both directions — the Music data has two profiles, and the Forum
profile works on both the clean and the noisy data fixtures.

